'''米高·凱雷·賀爾'''（{{lang-en|Michael C. Hall}}，{{bd|1971年|2月1日||}}）是一名美國電影及電視演員，因在[[HBO|HBO]]電視劇《[[六呎風雲|六呎風雲]]》中飾演大衛·費雪（{{lang|en|David Fisher}}）而漸露頭角，更在{{lang|en|Showtime}}電視劇《[[双面法医|双面法医]]》中飾德克斯特·摩根（{{lang|en|Dexter Morgan}}）而多次獲提名[[金球獎_(影視獎項)|金球獎]]、[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]及[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]，更於2010年憑此角贏得[[第67屆金球獎|第67屆]][[金球獎_(影視獎項)|金球獎]][[金球獎劇情類電視劇最佳男主角|劇情類電視劇最佳男主角]]及[[美國演員工會獎劇情類電視劇最佳男主角|美國演員工會獎劇情類電視劇最佳男主角]]。

==生平==
=== 早年 ===
賀爾全名{{lang|en|Michael Carlyle Hall}}，出生於[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[罗利_(北卡罗来纳州)|罗利]]，父親{{lang|en|William Carlyle}}是[[IBM|IBM]]職員，母親{{lang|en|Janice Styons}}是中學訓導老師。<ref name="ref05">{{cite news|last=Tallmer|first=Jerry|coauthors=|title=Take a girl in a tutu, a man in a suit, and just add writer|pages=|publisher=The Villager|date=2005-10-26|url=http://www.thevillager.com/villager_130/takeagirlinatutu.html|accessdate=2009-09-11|archive-date=2018-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731093301/http://thevillager.com/villager_130/takeagirlinatutu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>賀爾本來還有一個姊姊，卻在賀爾出生前已早歿，而賀爾的父親更於1982年賀爾11歲時因[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]逝去。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804736570/bio |title=Yahoo biography |accessdate=2010-02-16 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629010335/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804736570/bio |dead-url=no }}</ref>

賀爾中學在位於[[罗利_(北卡罗来纳州)|罗利]]的{{lang|en|Ravenscroft High School}}就讀，1989年畢業<ref>[http://www.ravenscroft.org/page.cfm?p=66&newsid=1172 Alumni News & Events] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602132300/http://www.ravenscroft.org/page.cfm?p=66 |date=2013-06-02 }}</ref>；大學則在{{tsl|en|Earlham College||厄爾漢學院}}就讀，1993年畢業；隨後在[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]修讀[[藝術創作碩士|藝術創作碩士]]學位。

===私人生活===
2002年，賀爾與同是演員的{{tsl|en|Amy Spanger|艾美·史班傑}}結婚，兩人婚後曾在[[百老匯|百老匯]]音樂劇《[[芝加哥_(音樂劇)|芝加哥]]》中同台演出，但五年後卻以離婚收場。

2008年12月31日，賀爾和同在《[[双面法医|双面法医]]》演出的[[珍妮佛·卡本特|珍妮佛·卡本特]]結婚。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20251400,00.html |title=Dexter siblings Michael C. Hall and Jennifer Carpenter are now real-life spouses |accessdate=2010-02-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064239/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20251400,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/watch_with_kristin/b78384_michael_c_hall_jennifer_carpenter_are.html Michael C. Hall and Jennifer Carpenter are Married] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/watch_with_kristin/b78384_michael_c_hall_jennifer_carpenter_are.html |date=20110713074014 }} E! online, January 10, 2009</ref>

2010年1月13日，賀爾的經紀人證實賀爾患上[[霍奇金病|霍奇金病]]（[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]的一種），賀爾的病況雖在接受治療後已緩解<ref>{{cite news |first=Lynn |last=Elber |title='Dexter' Star Hall Being Treated for Cancer |date=2010-01-13 |work=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20336663,00.html |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archive-date=2016-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422033118/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20336663,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但仍未能停止治療<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20336663,00.html|title=Dexter's Michael C. Hall Has Cancer|work=people.com|accessdate=2010-02-16|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422033118/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20336663,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。賀爾因接受[[化学疗法|化学疗法]]後脫髮，而需在同月舉辦的[[第67屆金球獎|第67屆金球獎]]及[[第16屆美國演員工會獎|第16屆美國演員工會獎]]的兩個頒獎典禮上戴上帽子。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/new-york-times-blogger-mocks-michael-c-halls-cap-without-knowing-he-had-cancer/story-e6frg30c-1225821699621 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-02-16 |archive-date=2015-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904153512/http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/new-york-times-blogger-mocks-michael-c-halls-cap-without-knowing-he-had-cancer/story-e6frg30c-1225821699621 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年12月，賀爾和珍妮佛·卡本特发布声明，在分居“一段时间”后，他们已提出了离婚。<ref name="EW1213">{{cite news|url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/12/13/michael-c-hall-jennifer-carpenter-divorce/|title='Dexter' stars Michael C. Hall, Jennifer Carpenter file for divorce (EW exclusive)|last=Snierson|first=Dan|date=13 December  2010|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=14 December 2010|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015044422/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/12/13/michael-c-hall-jennifer-carpenter-divorce/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

